	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td width="10%" nowrap="nowrap">Post subject:&nbsp;</td>
		<td><b></b></td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />VirtuaNes sort of emulates Gyromite. Basically, the screen would flash, the robot would push some buttons on the second controller causing the columns to change their positions. VirtuaNES does the second-controller-pushing for you.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


	<hr width="85%" />

